"0.9``, ``noise=0.6–0.8``, ``static_bands=0.4–0.6``, ``softness<=0.2``, ja "
"aseta ``bleed`` noin 0.3:een."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:387
msgid ""
"**Color fringing only**: raise ``bleed`` (about 0.5) and keep other controls "
"low."
msgstr ""
