# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:795
msgid ""
"The Crop effect removes unwanted outer areas from the video frame, allowing "
"you to focus on a particular part of the shot, change the aspect ratio, or "
"remove distracting elements from the edges of the frame. This effect is the "
"primary method for cropping a Clip in OpenShot. The ``left``, ``right``, "
